<https://maytetoscano.github.io/bblocks-bioclima/> a skos:ConceptScheme,
        dcat:Catalog,
        bblocks:BBlocksRegister ;
    rdfs:label "Building Blocks - BioClima OGC Building Blocks" ;
    dct:abstract """Interactive BioClima viewer: https://maytetoscano.github.io/bblocks-bioclima/viewer/

Register of OGC Building Blocks for Essential Biodiversity Variables (EBVs),
derived indicators, bioclimatic zonification, data provenance and policy
alignment with the Kunming-Montreal GBF. The pilot dataset is the Start of
Vegetation Active Period in Finland (2001-2018).
"""^^<https://www.w3.org/ns/iana/media-types/text/markdown> ;
    dct:description """**Interactive map viewer:** https://maytetoscano.github.io/bblocks-bioclima/viewer/

**Classified registry by family:** https://maytetoscano.github.io/bblocks-bioclima/viewer/registry.html

**OGC Building Blocks viewer:** https://maytetoscano.github.io/bblocks-bioclima/bblocks/

This register defines BioClima-specific building blocks on top of the
OGC CoverageJSON community standard. It includes:

- A profile of CoverageJSON for BioClima EBV datasets.
- Generic schemas for EBV records and indicator records.
- Concrete EBV datasets for Finnish coniferous and deciduous vegetation.
- The Phenological Change Indicator (PCI) and its bioclimatic zonification,
  each with a Python implementation that the CI can re-run automatically.
- A multilingual SKOS/RDF ontology building block used by EBVs, indicators,
  policy alignment, provenance and zonification records.
- W3C PROV-O provenance schemas for both EBVs and indicators.
- Policy alignment schemas linking indicators to Kunming-Montreal GBF
  targets and SDG 15.
"""^^<https://www.w3.org/ns/iana/media-types/text/markdown> ;
    dct:modified "2026-05-18T07:32:44.776893"^^xsd:dateTime ;
